{"word":"G2015 - ἐπιφάνεια - epipháneia - ep-if-an'-i-ah - Appearing","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιφάνεια</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epipháneia</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-if-an'-i-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Appearing</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிரசன்னம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"an appearing, appearance"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2016 - ἐπιφανής - epiphanḗs - ep-if-an-ace'/2016\">G2016</a>; a <i>manifestation</i>, that is, (specifically) the <i>advent</i> of Christ (past or future): - appearing, brightness.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1718/1718\">G1718</a>, <a href=\"#/G2014/2014\">G2014</a>, <a href=\"#/G2015/2015\">G2015</a>, <a href=\"#/G2016/2016\">G2016</a>, <a href=\"#/G5316/5316\">G5316</a>, <a href=\"#/G5318/5318\">G5318</a>, <a href=\"#/G5319/5319\">G5319</a>, <a href=\"#/G5320/5320\">G5320</a>, <a href=\"#/G5321/5321\">G5321</a>, <a href=\"#/G5322/5322\">G5322</a>, <a href=\"#/G5324/5324\">G5324</a>, <a href=\"#/G5325/5325\">G5325</a>, <a href=\"#/G5326/5326\">G5326</a>"}]}